00:39:33,751 --> 00:39:37,684
<font color="yellow">I became a lawyer so that I can be
of strength on the side of the weak.</font>

593
00:39:39,110 --> 00:39:40,985
<font color="yellow">I want to do my best to help them.</font>

594
00:39:41,594 --> 00:39:45,842
<font color="yellow">I'm just worried about you having
to go against Janghaenggo.</font>

595
00:39:46,383 --> 00:39:49,617
<font color="yellow">Think how you would feel if lawyers
turned away from you in this situation.</font>

596
00:39:50,282 --> 00:39:51,614
<font color="yellow">It would be very difficult.</font>

597
00:39:52,774 --> 00:39:55,257
<font color="yellow">And this is one case I can fight.</font>

598
00:39:56,126 --> 00:40:00,484
<font color="yellow">I'm preparing hard for this,
