657
00:44:04,137 --> 00:44:10,889
<font color="yellow">I lived in Chung-guyok,
Changgwang Street.</font>

658
00:44:12,200 --> 00:44:15,891
<font color="yellow">Oh, Chung-guyok,
Changgwang Street?</font>

659
00:44:15,916 --> 00:44:19,864
<font color="yellow">I know that's a place
where wealthy families live in.</font>

660
00:44:22,223 --> 00:44:25,098
<font color="yellow">It didn't seem like you
had lived a difficult life.</font>

661
00:44:25,489 --> 00:44:27,012
<font color="yellow">I guess I was right.</font>

662
00:44:28,997 --> 00:44:34,957
<font color="yellow">Are your parents
still alive in North Korea?</font>

663
00:44:37,364 --> 00:44:41,995
<font color="yellow">I had a mother-in-law,
