664
00:44:43,106 --> 00:44:45,402
<font color="yellow">As for my son and husband...</font>

665
00:44:47,504 --> 00:44:48,949
<font color="yellow">while we were escaping...</font>

666
00:44:49,887 --> 00:44:50,887
<font color="yellow">Oh, dear.</font>

667
00:44:51,879 --> 00:44:55,009
<font color="yellow">I already heard what had happened
to your son and husband.</font>

668
00:44:55,801 --> 00:44:58,895
<font color="yellow">I was shameless to
bring up your family again.</font>

669
00:45:00,645 --> 00:45:03,951
<font color="yellow">Since I'm growing old,
