670
00:45:03,976 --> 00:45:07,208
<font color="yellow">once the topic of
our home country comes up.</font>

671
00:45:07,926 --> 00:45:11,731
<font color="yellow">No, it's fine.
It's gotten a lot better now.</font>

672
00:45:12,528 --> 00:45:13,528
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

673
00:45:13,997 --> 00:45:19,616
<font color="yellow">If you have a firm heart and work hard,
