674
00:45:21,515 --> 00:45:22,515
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

675
00:45:24,843 --> 00:45:26,896
<font color="yellow">It's fine. Feel free to answer it.</font>

676
00:45:33,249 --> 00:45:34,350
<font color="yellow">Hi, it's me.</font>

677
00:45:35,241 --> 00:45:40,438
<font color="yellow">Mom, I finished work near the noodle restaurant.
