680
00:45:49,890 --> 00:45:50,890
<font color="yellow">Don't get lost.</font>

681
00:45:52,062 --> 00:45:53,062
<font color="yellow">Bye.</font>

682
00:46:20,952 --> 00:46:21,952
<font color="yellow">You!</font>

683
00:46:22,202 --> 00:46:24,213
<font color="yellow">Why are you coming down?
