00:46:30,194 --> 00:46:33,427
<font color="yellow">All right. I got it, so don't
you dare take one more step.</font>

686
00:46:33,702 --> 00:46:35,369
<font color="yellow">You better not come down!</font>

687
00:46:35,394 --> 00:46:38,483
<font color="yellow">Maid! Get Hee-ra some water!</font>

688
00:46:38,904 --> 00:46:41,382
<font color="yellow">Fill up a bottle up to
