691
00:46:49,858 --> 00:46:52,530
<font color="yellow">If I die, you can do
whatever you want with me!</font>

692
00:46:52,717 --> 00:46:56,591
<font color="yellow">Go ahead and sell me to a
congressman's son or a dermatologist!</font>

693
00:47:00,606 --> 00:47:05,035
<font color="yellow">That little brat.
What am I supposed to do with her?</font>

694
00:47:08,067 --> 00:47:10,926
<font color="yellow">Hee-ra, how do I look in this outfit?</font>

695
00:47:13,520 --> 00:47:16,530
<font color="yellow">Why bother asking? It must be difficult
