696
00:47:16,555 --> 00:47:18,350
<font color="yellow">Really? Is it that bad?</font>

697
00:47:18,895 --> 00:47:21,977
<font color="yellow">Gosh, what do I do?
Today is an important day.</font>

698
00:47:26,036 --> 00:47:28,079
<font color="yellow">What do you mean what do you do?
Of course you</font>

699
00:47:28,104 --> 00:47:30,146
<font color="yellow">have to change into
something more fashionable.</font>

700
00:47:30,895 --> 00:47:32,565
<font color="yellow">Should I wear a trench coat?</font>

701
00:47:34,200 --> 00:47:36,895
<font color="yellow">How can you wear
a trench coat in this weather?</font>

702
00:47:37,660 --> 00:47:40,533
<font color="yellow">Hee-dong, do you remember
the brand-name cardigan</font>

703
00:47:40,558 --> 00:47:43,487
<font color="yellow">that mom bought for dad
last year for his birthday?</font>

704
00:47:45,391 --> 00:47:47,976
<font color="yellow">Dad's cardigan? Yes! The blue one?</font>

705
00:47:48,125 --> 00:47:49,961
<font color="yellow">That's right.</font>

706
00:47:49,986 --> 00:47:55,081
<font color="yellow">Ask mom to find that one for you.
