725
00:49:34,031 --> 00:49:36,558
<font color="yellow">If you hadn't contacted me today,</font>

726
00:49:36,583 --> 00:49:39,334
<font color="yellow">I would've confidently marched into
your home and saved you.</font>

727
00:49:39,992 --> 00:49:41,813
<font color="yellow">Of course we'll be
able to see each other!</font>

728
00:49:44,078 --> 00:49:45,078
<font color="yellow">Really?</font>

729
00:49:45,344 --> 00:49:46,764
<font color="yellow">Yes, really.</font>

730
00:49:47,234 --> 00:49:49,489
<font color="yellow">It doesn't matter if
they refuse to let me in</font>

731
00:49:49,514 --> 00:49:51,768
<font color="yellow">or spray salt on me.
