735
00:50:03,875 --> 00:50:04,875
<font color="yellow">No!</font>

736
00:50:05,508 --> 00:50:06,854
<font color="yellow">I won't be able to live!</font>

737
00:50:08,641 --> 00:50:09,641
<font color="yellow">Hee-ra!</font>

738
00:50:09,666 --> 00:50:10,666
<font color="yellow">Yes, Jang-soo!</font>

739
00:50:11,000 --> 00:50:13,107
<font color="yellow">Then let's never be apart now.</font>

740
00:50:13,781 --> 00:50:17,029
<font color="yellow">From this moment on,
we'll be together forever!</font>

741
00:50:18,828 --> 00:50:21,140
<font color="yellow">Yes! Together forever!</font>

742
00:50:41,492 --> 00:50:44,797
<font color="yellow">Please do my hair and make-up lightly
