743
00:50:45,969 --> 00:50:47,372
<font color="yellow">As innocent as possible.</font>

744
00:50:47,727 --> 00:50:48,727
<font color="yellow">Yes, miss.</font>

745
00:51:08,570 --> 00:51:09,570
<font color="yellow">Hello.</font>

746
00:51:09,836 --> 00:51:10,836
<font color="yellow">Hello.</font>

747
00:51:11,180 --> 00:51:12,470
<font color="yellow">Do you need something?</font>

748
00:51:12,953 --> 00:51:14,328
<font color="yellow">I need a gift.</font>

749
00:51:15,422 --> 00:51:17,280
<font color="yellow">What kind of flowers do women like?</font>

750
00:51:17,991 --> 00:51:20,775
<font color="yellow">Who are they for? What's her age?</font>

751
00:51:21,781 --> 00:51:23,581
<font color="yellow">She's in her late twenties.</font>

752
00:51:25,711 --> 00:51:30,617
<font color="yellow">I would like flowers for
