753
00:52:51,596 --> 00:52:52,596
<font color="yellow">Come in.</font>

754
00:52:52,849 --> 00:52:53,849
<font color="yellow">Excuse me.</font>

755
00:52:58,307 --> 00:52:59,307
<font color="yellow">Here.</font>

756
00:52:59,815 --> 00:53:00,815
<font color="yellow">Oh, my.</font>

757
00:53:01,681 --> 00:53:04,319
<font color="yellow">Thank you. You didn't
