758
00:53:17,322 --> 00:53:18,322
<font color="yellow">But...</font>

759
00:53:20,025 --> 00:53:21,025
<font color="yellow">is it this one?</font>

760
00:53:21,697 --> 00:53:23,009
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

761
00:53:24,447 --> 00:53:25,447
<font color="yellow">I need a chair.</font>

762
00:53:25,705 --> 00:53:28,638
<font color="yellow">I do have a chair,
