763
00:53:28,908 --> 00:53:29,908
<font color="yellow">It's fine.</font>

764
00:53:37,157 --> 00:53:38,157
<font color="yellow">Be careful.</font>

765
00:53:47,830 --> 00:53:49,044
<font color="yellow">Thank you.</font>

766
00:54:04,189 --> 00:54:05,189
<font color="yellow">Are you done?</font>

767
00:54:05,767 --> 00:54:07,285
<font color="yellow">Can you turn on the lights?</font>

768
00:54:07,310 --> 00:54:08,310
<font color="yellow">Sure.</font>

769
00:54:10,494 --> 00:54:12,684
<font color="yellow">Wow! The light came on!</font>

770
00:54:15,205 --> 00:54:16,345
<font color="yellow">Thank you!</font>

771
00:54:17,861 --> 00:54:19,589
<font color="yellow">- The case.
