772
00:54:26,393 --> 00:54:27,593
<font color="yellow">I think it's done.</font>

773
00:54:27,838 --> 00:54:29,007
<font color="yellow">Thank you.</font>

774
00:54:30,736 --> 00:54:31,736
<font color="yellow">Oh my gosh!</font>

775
00:54:40,744 --> 00:54:41,744
<font color="yellow">Oh, my.</font>

776
00:54:44,471 --> 00:54:48,771
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry. I should have gotten
